<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p>Virotikly respects your privacy. We do not collect or store personal data without your consent.</p>

<p>All TikTok authentication is handled securely through TikTok’s official OAuth system. We only access the data necessary to provide our services.</p>

<p>We do not share user data with third parties.</p>

<p>By using Virotikly, you agree to this privacy policy.</p>
